  <brief_title>BECOME PATIENTS IN THE EMERGENCIES OF UHC POITIERS</brief_title>
  <acronym>DEPAUG</acronym>
  <official_title>ANALYSIS OF THE BECOME OF THE PATIENTS ADDRESSED BY THEIR GENERAL PRACTITIONER TO EMERGENCIES OF UHC POITIERS</official_title>
